        <h3 class="rule">McDonald Family House Rules.</h3>
        
        <ul class ="Rule">
            <li>Honour God in everything you do (1 Corinthians 10:31)</li><br>
            <li>Obey your parents on the first ask (Ephesians 6:1-3)</li><br>
            <li>Do not talk back to your parents (1 Timothy 5:17)</li><br>
            <li>Treat things with care (Proverbs 27:23-24)</li><br>
            <li>Say only positive and building-up things (Ephesians 4:29)</li><br>
            <li>Always tell the truth (Ephesians 4:25)</li><br>
            <li>Remember the Fruits of the Spirit (Galatians 5:22-23)</li><br>
            <li>Put others before yourself, remember J-O-Y (Jesus first, others second, yourself last)<br> (Philippians 2:3-4)</li><br>
            <li> Be grateful (Ephesians 5:20)</li><br>
            <li>Remember your manners (Titus 3:2)</li><br>
            <li>Eat in your seat and remember table manners (Sirach 31:12-18)</li><br>
            <li>Help keep our house clean (Luke 11:25)</li><br>
            <li>Do not keep secrets from your parents (Ecclesiastes 12:14)</li><br>
            </ul>
        
